# mod_irida_project
# update fields on an existing IRIDA project via PATCH /api/projects/{id}
# confirmed working as non-admin on VIGASP 23.01.3 - RBAC gap, see GitHub issue #12
#
# usage: mod_irida_project PROJECT_ID [--name NAME] [--description DESC] [--organism ORG] [--genome-size SIZE] [--min-coverage MIN] [--max-coverage MAX]
#
# at least one optional field must be provided
#
# example: mod_irida_project 155:KOTOP --description "new description" --organism "Trollus norvegicus"
